data.description: Well-maintained split level in the Van Lear Manor subdivision! Featuring 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths. Eat-in kitchen with oak cabinets. Dining room with hardwood floors. Living room with new LVP flooring. Bedrooms on upper level with carpet flooring and double closets. Jack-&-Jill bathroom with separate tub, separate shower and two separate sinks. Finished basement with family room and wood stove, full bath with double sinks and soaking tub, walkout level to side yard. Newly installed radon system. Spacious back yard that's partially fenced. 2-car garage with new garage doors, extra workshop space and access to pull down attic. Williamsport school district. Close access to I-81 and I-70. Seller willing to provide $10k closing help! Schedule your tour today!
